Package: sims
Title: Simulate Data from 'JAGS' or R Code
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Audrey", "Beliveau", , "audrey.beliveau@uwaterloo.ca", "aut"),
    person("Joe", "Thorley", , "joe@poissonconsulting.ca", c("aut", "cre"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-7683-4592"))
    )
Description: Generates data from 'JAGS' or R code for use in simulation studies.
    The data are returned as an 'nlist::nlists' object and/or saved to file as 
    individual '.rds' files. 
    Parallelization is implemented using the 'future' package.
    Progress is reported using the 'progressr' package.
License: GPL-3
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.6)
Imports:
    stats,
    yesno,
    chk,
    nlist,
    parallel,
    future.apply
Suggests: 
